parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can cause the doors to open unexpectedly while driving, leading to accidents or injuries, or prevent the doors from opening in emergency situations, putting occupants at risk.
symptoms: Doors open unexpectedly while driving
doors cannot be opened from the inside or outside
door handles malfunction
doors get stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Acceleration and Cruise Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents or injuries, and the malfunctioning cruise control can lead to unintended acceleration.
symptoms: Sudden and unexpected acceleration
cruise control malfunctions
haptic touch-sensitive control on the steering wheel triggers accidental acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The software and electronic system glitches can cause distractions, malfunctions, and safety concerns, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Software system reboots unexpectedly
dashboard information disappears
radio display goes blank
glitches affect various components of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shattering of the rear window can cause injuries, damage, and safety concerns, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Rear window shatters unexpectedly
defrost system malfunctions
tempered glass breaks inward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning ESC can cause distractions, loss of control, and safety concerns, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: ESC activates briefly under normal conditions
ESC flashes warning lights
vehicle handling changes suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unusual Noises and Lack of Resolution
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unusual noises can cause distractions, discomfort, and safety concerns, and the lack of resolution from the manufacturer can lead to frustration and anxiety.
symptoms: Loud
high-pitched sounds coming from the vehicle
no resolution available from the manufacturer.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Pedal Freezing and Faulty Sensor
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake pedal freezing and faulty sensor can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal freezes intermittently
the sensor flashes red and warns of brake failure
the vehicle does not detect obstacles in autonomous driving mode
and the front brakes seize up after driving in the rain.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Parking Brake and Auto Hold Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The parking brake and auto hold issues can cause the vehicle to roll away or lose control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The parking brake does not engage
the vehicle rolls away on an incline
and the auto hold feature is not available or malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Regenerative Braking and Adaptive Cruise Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The regenerative braking and adaptive cruise control issues can cause the vehicle to lose control or slow down unexpectedly, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The regenerative braking turns off when applying the brakes
leaving only friction brakes to slow or stop the vehicle
and the adaptive cruise control malfunctions or disengages.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ESC issues can cause the vehicle to lose control or brake unexpectedly, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The ESC activates unnecessarily
causing the brake pedal to collapse
uneven braking
and loss of control
especially on curvy roads or during low-speed corners.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure and Loss of Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake failure and loss of control can cause accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brakes do not respond or fail to engage
causing the vehicle to crash or lose control
and the airbags may not deploy.
